title: Analytic Symphony Series
additional-note: The earliest active issue renewal we found was filed in a Books volume of the CCE, rather than a Periodicals volume.  Issues might also be renewed in Music volumes, which we have not systematically surveyed. Number 8 (Mendelssohn's Symphony in A Minor, edited by Percy Goetschius) was originally registered in 1928 under Music, but we have not found a timely renewal for it in that category, or under Books or Periodicals.
